{"tid":858563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港真係冇得救","createTime":"2018-10-12T01:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T08:21:02.000Z","uid":207208,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"474b9dafdd7df7f0d59288568a0eae91f97a88db","tid":858563,"uid":207208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"尋日仲好多人討論緊一萬億既事<br />\n仍然有人會諗下點抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者嘗試得到外界既注意<br />\n但係今日 已經冇人再討論<br />\n雖然話 就咁討論 對件事都冇幫助<br />\n但有討論 證明大家仲會關心<br />\n<br />\n雖然四年前雨革失敗令好多人灰心咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近年港共政權又大力打壓民主自由<br />\n令到好多人寧願只係返工返學 行屍走肉<br />\n乜都唔理唔想知 但係因為一次失敗<br />\n就唔再嘗試？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要屌我鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我做唔到啲咩 但真係想多啲人關心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人 幾時先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/091101_c8700f104f91bc70c52a4e55f159f76f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F091101_c8700f104f91bc70c52a4e55f159f76f.png&h=8aeb6cc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0fba358309105db1de9e9cad658a5ec0828533a","tid":858563,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"其實我諗到點解政府要搞人工島。<br />\n<br />\n香港樓價貴，房屋供應少係事實。<br />\n<br />\n搞新界北，<br />\n班原居民會嘈，早前又有反新界北發展計劃，<br />\n又有乜中港融合的陰謀論。<br />\n<br />\n搞西貢，移山和交通都一樣好貴。<br />\n<br />\n搞九龍填海，保護海港條例block左。<br />\n<br />\n搞港島南，班有錢佬反對。<br />\n（政府怕得罪富商，政治面前窮人含撚的明證。）<br />\n<br />\n搞南大嶼山，交通不便。<br />\n<br />\n所以諗左東大嶼，交通夠方便。<br />\n去中環，出九龍，去機場都非常方便。<br />\n但就貴到hihi。"},{"pid":"e8a7c97e27ca66a7ddf8c7b0725c3e0069bc6cbb","tid":858563,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0fba358309105db1de9e9cad658a5ec0828533a","tid":858563,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"其實我諗到點解政府要搞人工島。<br />\n<br />\n香港樓價貴，房屋供應少係事實。<br />\n<br />\n搞新界北，<br />\n班原居民會嘈，早前又有反新界北發展計劃，<br />\n又有乜中港融合的陰謀論。<br />\n<br />\n搞西貢，移山和交通都一樣好貴。<br />\n<br />\n搞九龍填海，保護海港條例block左。<br />\n<br />\n搞港島南，班有錢佬反對。<br />\n（政府怕得罪富商，政治面前窮人含撚的明證。）<br />\n<br />\n搞南大嶼山，交通不便。<br />\n<br />\n所以諗左東大嶼，交通夠方便。<br />\n去中環，出九龍，去機場都非常方便。<br />\n但就貴到hihi。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae70f4bfcbfdb2bce3be1054d23a729fe8bdfe6","tid":858563,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"呢度有個網<br />\n講香港土地供應<br />\n寫得不錯<br />\n大陸網黎<br />\n似乎大陸仔對香港<br />\n比香港人對香港更了解<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32628240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F32628240&d=UT4wyXMF1UWjDgMt49VIJhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ec412cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32628240</a>"},{"pid":"51e5f2a2c7ab73539b46088f9eeba8b5a6d1da9e","tid":858563,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bae70f4bfcbfdb2bce3be1054d23a729fe8bdfe6","tid":858563,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"呢度有個網<br />\n講香港土地供應<br />\n寫得不錯<br />\n大陸網黎<br />\n似乎大陸仔對香港<br />\n比香港人對香港更了解<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32628240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F32628240&d=UT4wyXMF1UWjDgMt49VIJhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ec412cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32628240</a>"},"citedBy